    "These tasks should be practical and scenario-based to accurately gauge the agents' capabilities.",
    "They should assess a wide range of competencies, from technical execution to critical thinking.",
    "For example, in evaluating a DevOps engineer, the agent might be tasked with automating a deployment pipeline using tools like Jenkinsfoot_10 or Docker 11, or troubleshooting a continuous integration failure.",
